methods.name: CreateOrUpdate
methods.description:
CreateOrUpdate should only be used from within the application
will check if tenant already exists and updates if necessary, otherwise create a new tenant

fields.name: page_token
fields.description: page_token is used for pagination, if unset only the first page is returned, the list response contains then token for the next page.
fields.label: optional

fields.name: count
fields.description: count is the number of results returned per page, if no given server side defaults apply
fields.label: optional

fields.name: next_page_token
fields.description: next_page_token is used for pagination, returns the next page to be fetched and must then be provided in the list request.
